import Button from "../UI/Button/Button"

const BillCalculation = (props) => {



    return (

        <form>
            <label>Bill</label>
            <input value="0.00"></input>
            <label>Select Tip %</label>
            <Button>5%</Button>
            <label>Number of People</label>
            <input value="1"></input>
        </form>
    )
}

export default BillCalculation
